The paper deals with visual saliency detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning techniques for saliency detection also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of end-to-end learning, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
